### DFS (Depth-First Search)

**DFS** explores as far as possible along each branch before backtracking.

**Order** (preorder ‚Äì Node, Left, Right):  
`A ‚Üí B ‚Üí D ‚Üí E ‚Üí C ‚Üí F ‚Üí G`

