### üîê How to Get Razorpay Test Key
1. Go to [https://razorpay.com/](https://razorpay.com/)
2. Create a **free developer account**
3. From the Dashboard, go to:
   - Settings ‚Üí API Keys ‚Üí Generate Key
4. Use the **test key** in place of `"rzp_test_YourTestKeyHere"`

